body:
Okay so commissions!!!

Im doing commissions now and like yeah heres some info for like what i do yeah

Okay this was fast i promise my art is usually better!!!

But okay so prices!

For my doodle art in that weird pixel style no color

Head and shoulders: 2$

Most of the body like waist up or knees up: 3$

Full body: 5$

For my doodle art in that weird pixel style WITH color

Head and shoulders: 3$

Most of the body like waist up or knees up: 4$

Full body: 7$

For color and colorless 2$ more for each extra character!

And for my digital painting style 10$ for that and 5$ for each extra character in that!

Now for some examples of my art!!!

My pixely doodle style:

Digital painting style:

What i will draw:

  • Characters from other fandoms
  • OCs
  • Idk i can try to draw you
  • Uhhhh idk

What i won’t draw:

  • Nsfw
  • Any ships thar involve abuse, pedophilla, incest, etc.
  • Idk hopefully yall get it

But yeah thanks for coming to my ted talk message me if you want my art please reblog this!!!
